Okay, there's something I really need to point out to Bregalad, something that's been bugging me for quite a while now.<br /><br />There is no such thing as "mirroiting". The word you are looking for is "mirroring" (derived from the word "mirror").<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=7">Quietust</a> — Sat Dec 25, 2004 10:12 pm</p><hr />
